{
  "stem": "12768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even though it was pork, my mother said to, to all the kids and to whoever was sick, eat it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you cannot-- the most important thing is to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So whatever we can get and eat and take, do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think my mother-- again, I say her name, Martha Lerno-- was probably one of the key factors in-- that a lot of people knew her and knew.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was, she was really with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even once she come back, I must say that my mother, of course, had suffered by it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was internally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that-- you couldn't see through the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When time came, like I said, there was an hour before they were told that those buses are here for you guys.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they didn't take anybody else and just whatever was Norwegian or Swedish and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my uncle's brother was a bachelor, had met a, a lady.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can only say her first name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know it was Hanke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was from Czechoslovakia somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And somehow, she got to Denmark with this group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And how she did it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my uncle's brother married her afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she became Hanke Abrahamson, so-- But that was how they were driven to Germany and into Denmark and then over to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in Sweden, they went to health checks up and medical treatments and all for malnutrition and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Of course, they weren't as bad as [INAUDIBLE] at the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so there was French prisoners came up through Denmark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And if you saw bus fulls of just absolutely skeletons.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
